To an experience filled with fun, joy, love and many quirky annoying laughs 🥵🌸🧿❤️🥰

#1960s #bombay #smallseries #vintageaesthetic #hindistories

60s in 2022!!
Presenting the poster of my first series, alongside barbie di and nitin😍. Proud to be a part of it. Cant thank barbie dii @instabarbierajput enough for this🤗. Thankyou for showing so much faith in me and giving me such a beautiful opportunity. My heart is filled with gratitude today as I see myself in the poster🙏🏻🧿. Barbie di, You will not regret this.🐒 

Nitin, what do I say, you are an absolute example of partner in crime😎. Thanks for being as crazy as me. It was so much fun to develop this charachter with you. Thankyou for being you, And helping me with everything!❤️

A big thanks to blake @blakedtunes 🤗thankyouuuuu for creating magic,You’re an amazing soul❤️. @kpangare for designing the sound. @shimlahues for creating this beautiful artwork❤️

Thankyou barbie di for turning my dreams into reality. This is big for me and super special. Feeling proud. Love you. ❤️

Grateful for everything 🙏🏻🧿

To my Instagram fam, do watch it and show some love ❤️
